Here, we copy the source code to our repository instead of using a Git submodule to simplify compilation and make the source code self-contained. We also remove the unused parts.

url: https://github.com/NVIDIA/cutlass.git
commit: dc4817921edda44a549197ff3a9dcf5df0636e7b

operations:
```
rm -rf cutlass.org
git clone https://github.com/NVIDIA/cutlass.git cutlass.org
pushd cutlass.org
git checkout dc4817921edda44a549197ff3a9dcf5df0636e7b
popd

mkdir -p cutlass

mv cutlass.org/include/ cutlass/ 
rm cutlass.org/ -rf
```
